cross: Rhyncattleanthe San Diego Sunset x Cattleya loddigesii

measurements.description: Seven slightly crowded flowers on one upright 16-cm inflorescence; sepals and petals cream overlaid dark pink, green sepal tips; lip slightly ruffled, cream overlaid dark pink, darker blotches middle, throat yellow; column cream pink edge at anther cap, anther cap cream; substance firm; texture slightly crystalline.
